sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Investor
    participant ERC as ERC1155Facet
    participant Freeze as FreezeStorage
    participant Asset as AssetStorage
    participant Balance as ERC1155Storage
    participant Router as ComplianceRouterFacet
    participant Module as IComplianceModule
    participant Supply as SupplyStorage

    User->>ERC: safeTransferFrom(from, to, tokenId, amount)

    Note over ERC: Step 1 — Global Checks
    ERC->>Freeze: globalPaused?
    Freeze-->>ERC: false
    ERC->>Freeze: globalFreeze[from]?
    Freeze-->>ERC: false
    ERC->>Freeze: globalFreeze[to]?
    Freeze-->>ERC: false

    Note over ERC: Step 2 — Asset Checks
    ERC->>Asset: configs[tokenId].exists?
    Asset-->>ERC: true
    ERC->>Asset: configs[tokenId].paused?
    Asset-->>ERC: false
    ERC->>Freeze: assetFreeze[tokenId][from]?
    Freeze-->>ERC: false
    ERC->>Freeze: lockupExpiry[tokenId][from] <= now?
    Freeze-->>ERC: true

    Note over ERC: Step 3 — Balance Check
    ERC->>Balance: partitions[tokenId][from].free
    Balance-->>ERC: 1000
    ERC->>Freeze: frozenAmount[tokenId][from]
    Freeze-->>ERC: 200
    Note over ERC: available = 1000 - 200 = 800 >= amount ✓

    Note over ERC: Step 4 — Compliance Check
    ERC->>Asset: configs[tokenId].complianceModule
    Asset-->>ERC: 0xModuleAddr
    ERC->>Router: canTransfer(tokenId, from, to, amount)
    Router->>Module: canTransfer(tokenId, from, to, amount, "")
    Module-->>Router: (true, 0x0)
    Router-->>ERC: true ✓

    Note over ERC: Step 5 — Execute
    ERC->>Balance: from.free -= amount
    ERC->>Balance: to.free += amount
    ERC->>Supply: update holder tracking
    ERC-->>User: emit TransferSingle

    Note over ERC: Step 6 — Post-Hook
    ERC->>Router: transferred(tokenId, from, to, amount)
    Router->>Module: transferred(tokenId, from, to, amount)
